{"tid":1913032,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［屙咗成世都唔知］究竟屎既臭味係點嚟？","createTime":"2020-03-06T13:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T14:46:42.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e44220078df42189b901d05887744c175eff4cac","tid":1913032,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:18:28.000Z","msg":"係咩物質引起？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2717e5a2e3b3ede8f11ead3b4f2f7482708f38e","tid":1913032,"uid":169992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:27:24.000Z","msg":"硫"},{"pid":"99199bd9d18a28f3a0e108b1ce38721755b278c2","tid":1913032,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:43:09.000Z","msg":"處巴原來會開膠post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw, 係大腸入面嘅細菌"},{"pid":"f31387e93d0166e699721c65efa6052501f728b8","tid":1913032,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:44:31.000Z","msg":"細菌無氧呼吸<br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1279cfe3bba135289a1569e9136a8afa01a2d317","tid":1913032,"uid":306920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99199bd9d18a28f3a0e108b1ce38721755b278c2","tid":1913032,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:43:09.000Z","msg":"處巴原來會開膠post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw, 係大腸入面嘅細菌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:57:03.000Z","msg":"咁有時臭到仆街有時無乜味係因為咩<br />\n利申：餐餐飲食均衡，無多肉少菜"},{"pid":"7eb61e7b910cf9ef31af8376d8b3e43c5ed476ea","tid":1913032,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1279cfe3bba135289a1569e9136a8afa01a2d317","tid":1913032,"uid":306920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99199bd9d18a28f3a0e108b1ce38721755b278c2","tid":1913032,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:43:09.000Z","msg":"處巴原來會開膠post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw, 係大腸入面嘅細菌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:57:03.000Z","msg":"咁有時臭到仆街有時無乜味係因為咩<br />\n利申：餐餐飲食均衡，無多肉少菜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:00:54.000Z","msg":"熱氣嘅話，d屎同個口都臭d"},{"pid":"62dc9b9cd0d08a490bbdffc387e85d1df3faf885","tid":1913032,"uid":306920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7eb61e7b910cf9ef31af8376d8b3e43c5ed476ea","tid":1913032,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot